Title: Manifest Duality in Born-Infeld Theory

Authors: Ingemar Bengtsson (Stockholm)

Comments: 15 pages, Latex

Journal-ref: Int.J.Mod.Phys. A12 (1997) 4869-4880

Born-Infeld theory is formulated using an infinite set of gauge fields, alongthe lines of McClain, Wu and Yu. In this formulation electromagnetic duality isgenerated by a fully local functional. The resulting consistency problems areanalyzed and the formulation is shown to be consistent.